#: ../../index.md:5 46be3e8b729d4f89919c5e1fb08fd3cc
msgid ""
"Users open server-side folders as workspaces, browse and manage files, "
"and chat with AI grounded in workspace files via RAG (Retrieval-Augmented"
" Generation)."
msgstr "用户可以将服务器端文件夹作为工作空间打开，浏览和管理文件，并通过 RAG（检索增强生成）与基于工作空间文件的 AI 进行对话。"
